==Music==
The music of the film has been composed by Arifin Rumey. Music has been produced under the banner of [[Laser Vision]].<ref>{{cite news |script-title=বিশ্বজিৎকে নিয়ে স্বল্পদৈর্ঘ্য চলচ্চিত্র |trans-title= |url=http://www.banglanews24.com/fullnews/bn/281362.html |language=bn |newspaper=banglanews24 |accessdate=25 April 2014}}</ref>  The music was released on 10 April 2014. The album consists of 12 tracks.

